The vaccine candidate is currently in laboratory research, with human trials planned in July or August 2020.
Earlier that week, The Guardian reported that US President Donald Trump had offered CureVac "'a large sum of money' for exclusive access to the Covid-19 vaccine", which was protested by the German government.
